      "date": "2017-08-19 14:14:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe patch itself is fine. But I would suggest to use new LU ticket for this issue. LU-9894 is another failure instance of LU-9887, that is not related with the improper LFSCK types output.\n\nOr you can update the description of LU-9894 to describe the issue that is fixed by your patch to avoid misguiding.",
